com.undead_pixels.dungeon_bots.file.editor

Class LevelScriptSection

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.undead_pixels.dungeon_bots.file.editor.LevelScriptSection
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    FakeEditorStateSection, PlayerInitSection, TileRegionSection, WorldSizeSection

    public abstract class LevelScriptSection
extends java.lang.Object
    An arbitrary section of Lua code that is formatted in a specific way that the editor can parse and know that it will produce consistent results. This (inside of GameEditorState) can be used to both load and save levels, without running the full world.
